ol.li:
In your customization css
                add:*[class ~= "topic/table"] {
    hyphens: auto;
}

To except certain elements from beign hyphenated, use hyphens:none. In the next
                    example, we will exclude the keyword  elements from being
                    hyphenated:*[class ~= "topic/keyword"] {
    hyphens: none;
}
